{"id": "ChIJ_TQYZY_awoARAjrVzsNYoYo", "rating": 4.1, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 1262, "displayName": {"text": "Sea Harbour Seafood Restaurant", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Upscale go-to for traditional lunchtime dim sum & Cantonese seafood entrees for dinner.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ_TQYZY_awoARAjrVzsNYoYo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCUWNWQkJTSFJoVldrMlVXRXlkVkJmV1RscFdXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Every time I pass by this Cantonese restaurant at lunchtime, I always see a lot of customers waiting to be seated, so it seems like a very popular restaurant. I decided to try their dim sum. After waiting for over 30 minutes, I was finally seated and chose a few common dim sum dishes. Unfortunately, the taste was very average. While not bad, it was clearly overrated compared to the number of people waiting outside.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Every time I pass by this Cantonese restaurant at lunchtime, I always see a lot of customers waiting to be seated, so it seems like a very popular restaurant. I decided to try their dim sum. After waiting for over 30 minutes, I was finally seated and chose a few common dim sum dishes. Unfortunately, the taste was very average. While not bad, it was clearly overrated compared to the number of people waiting outside.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Paul T.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110538738313981170046/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdVl04ZmS0O2PqDnyiY0HQrExGG529OB-SXvWChDACnrnO4l54=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-30T08:37:08.371661484Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCUWNWQkJTSFJoVldrMlVXRXlkVkJmV1RscFdXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCUWNWQkJTSFJoVldrMlVXRXlkVkJmV1RscFdXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2da8f651834fd:0x8aa158c3ced53a02"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ_TQYZY_awoARAjrVzsNYoYo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201RGEyZHZUalpMYzJSZlVDMXpTRFF0TnpoeWJuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "​If you're planning a visit, be prepared for a crowd. We went for lunch and had a significant 35-minute wait to be seated. The dining room was buzzing and clearly very popular.\n​However, the reason for the queue is simple: this is some of the best and most authentic Chinese food I've had outside of mainland China. Everything we tried was fantastic, but the one dish you absolutely must order is the roasted pork. It's delicious: crispy skin, tender meat, and perfectly seasoned.\n​Go, but maybe try to get there a little before the lunch rush, or just accept the wait!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "​If you're planning a visit, be prepared for a crowd. We went for lunch and had a significant 35-minute wait to be seated. The dining room was buzzing and clearly very popular.\n​However, the reason for the queue is simple: this is some of the best and most authentic Chinese food I've had outside of mainland China. Everything we tried was fantastic, but the one dish you absolutely must order is the roasted pork. It's delicious: crispy skin, tender meat, and perfectly seasoned.\n​Go, but maybe try to get there a little before the lunch rush, or just accept the wait!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "MEILYNG HU", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101086573888163779428/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqMPNncwYy4_74-b5JinhKbpBFTl6q4E2CJ5pOA0ApUWFFZEff=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-27T20:51:10.036156598Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201RGEyZHZUalpMYzJSZlVDMXpTRFF0TnpoeWJuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201RGEyZHZUalpMYzJSZlVDMXpTRFF0TnpoeWJuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2da8f651834fd:0x8aa158c3ced53a02"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ_TQYZY_awoARAjrVzsNYoYo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205TGVqVmFiMjVmUzA1RldtUnhSak5zZVRWNk1rRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "The seafood porridge was completely flavorless—instead, it just tasted of raw scallions. The soy sauce chicken was decent, but the meat was undercooked and tough to chew. The tofu had an unpleasant taste of rancid oil. All in all, we didn't order a single dish that was satisfying.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The seafood porridge was completely flavorless—instead, it just tasted of raw scallions. The soy sauce chicken was decent, but the meat was undercooked and tough to chew. The tofu had an unpleasant taste of rancid oil. All in all, we didn't order a single dish that was satisfying.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "rain xia", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107402429244481093337/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW743la1GBBLcYkkorNl24R7YJD9BQE3ItjO7t2CF1zuSdWd44=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-20T04:50:02.476009232Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205TGVqVmFiMjVmUzA1RldtUnhSak5zZVRWNk1rRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205TGVqVmFiMjVmUzA1RldtUnhSak5zZVRWNk1rRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2da8f651834fd:0x8aa158c3ced53a02"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ_TQYZY_awoARAjrVzsNYoYo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201M2RtWk9SbkoxYjJGQ05sbHhkMDU2YjA5T2NXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Tucked away in the bustling LA dining scene, Sea Harbor consistently proves why it's a true institution for high-quality, authentic Cantonese-style Chinese cuisine. While the weekend dim sum is famous, I recently visited for dinner and was completely blown away by their specialty dishes, which feel like a step above standard Chinese fare.\nThe atmosphere is always lively—bustling but never overwhelming—making it perfect for family gatherings or celebratory dinners. The service is efficient and attentive, ensuring teacups are always full and dishes arrive quickly and piping hot.\nThe Trilogy of Excellence (Your Recommendations are Spot On):\n* Roast/Peking Duck: This is non-negotiable. The duck here is legendary. The skin shatters with the slightest pressure, giving way to incredibly tender, juicy meat. It’s prepared and carved perfectly, and the overall flavor is rich and complex. A benchmark duck for all of Southern California.\n* Crispy Fried Pigeon: If you've never tried it, this is the place. It's often overlooked, but Sea Harbor's preparation is flawless. The skin is deeply seasoned and crisp, and the meat is surprisingly tender and savory—a truly authentic and delicious experience that showcases the skill of the kitchen.\n* Signature Fried Fish Dish: The quality of their seafood shines brightly here and perfectly cooked. The exterior was lightly battered and wonderfully crisp, while the fish inside remained moist and flaky. You can taste the freshness, proving they source top-tier ingredients.\nSea Harbor is more than just a restaurant; it’s an experience in authentic Cantonese dining. If you are a serious fan of classic Chinese cuisine, and especially if you are looking to treat yourself to exceptional duck, unique delicacies like the pigeon, and  fried fish, don't walk, run there!  You won’t regret it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Tucked away in the bustling LA dining scene, Sea Harbor consistently proves why it's a true institution for high-quality, authentic Cantonese-style Chinese cuisine. While the weekend dim sum is famous, I recently visited for dinner and was completely blown away by their specialty dishes, which feel like a step above standard Chinese fare.\nThe atmosphere is always lively—bustling but never overwhelming—making it perfect for family gatherings or celebratory dinners. The service is efficient and attentive, ensuring teacups are always full and dishes arrive quickly and piping hot.\nThe Trilogy of Excellence (Your Recommendations are Spot On):\n* Roast/Peking Duck: This is non-negotiable. The duck here is legendary. The skin shatters with the slightest pressure, giving way to incredibly tender, juicy meat. It’s prepared and carved perfectly, and the overall flavor is rich and complex. A benchmark duck for all of Southern California.\n* Crispy Fried Pigeon: If you've never tried it, this is the place. It's often overlooked, but Sea Harbor's preparation is flawless. The skin is deeply seasoned and crisp, and the meat is surprisingly tender and savory—a truly authentic and delicious experience that showcases the skill of the kitchen.\n* Signature Fried Fish Dish: The quality of their seafood shines brightly here and perfectly cooked. The exterior was lightly battered and wonderfully crisp, while the fish inside remained moist and flaky. You can taste the freshness, proving they source top-tier ingredients.\nSea Harbor is more than just a restaurant; it’s an experience in authentic Cantonese dining. If you are a serious fan of classic Chinese cuisine, and especially if you are looking to treat yourself to exceptional duck, unique delicacies like the pigeon, and  fried fish, don't walk, run there!  You won’t regret it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Neon Pion", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110084512116821394543/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbMwGRbAwJno5xrbfdMQOYn2APd9w724GCUFzRE3R6i_p4UGZp=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-12T03:48:00.303587458Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201M2RtWk9SbkoxYjJGQ05sbHhkMDU2YjA5T2NXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201M2RtWk9SbkoxYjJGQ05sbHhkMDU2YjA5T2NXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2da8f651834fd:0x8aa158c3ced53a02"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ_TQYZY_awoARAjrVzsNYoYo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210Q1YxTlNXVmgzYm1JeU0zQjBWemhvZG5OaldXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I love this dim sum.  Must be one of the best if not the best.  Everyone I know that had been here also love this Dim Sum.  We live in OC but would drive here from time to time to eat here for dim sum.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love this dim sum.  Must be one of the best if not the best.  Everyone I know that had been here also love this Dim Sum.  We live in OC but would drive here from time to time to eat here for dim sum.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sherry T Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106382638729747689092/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ35kfg5H3I9e9hQ4bSwGMfX5CJjfZGyv72IMGG3CdyQfiYA7-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-28T22:16:41.361546360Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210Q1YxTlNXVmgzYm1JeU0zQjBWemhvZG5OaldXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210Q1YxTlNXVmgzYm1JeU0zQjBWemhvZG5OaldXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2da8f651834fd:0x8aa158c3ced53a02"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ_TQYZY_awoARAjrVzsNYoYo/photos/AWCwydhYcV4kfCsgxo93F664KjVbVFNSTKRwInA-usvGFTOmtuEWGppRDQL3HOy700F9rjARtj9yhxWyOwlymC6Bj28q4rqAN8YGRYNWkv1os38xoz-aDJRFEuAUB2VM2-4iSr_V7GNuRIrDQYRzBGBd5QKXbIMDV1T9zl9m43Bx0WSHrYpJ6NofmBeTYCC2gHyh